Name: Flume
Slogan: For those who love text

Theming
* Tint/foreground/background colors
* Typeface/line height

Offline/Online Switch
* Discover/Micro
* Notes/Blog
* Book/Docs
* Accounts
    * Profile/cover images
    * Biography text

Everything is publishable/searchable/reference-able. Self hosting
option, cant publish to public tho.

- Micro has
    - Linear comments
    - Hashtags
- Blog has
    - Likes/dislikes
    - Hierarchical comments
    - Tags
- Docs has
    - Acyclic dependent versioning
    - Chat
